# Branch Analysis & Sync Architecture Diagrams

## System Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "CLI Layer"
        A[main.py] --> B[commands.py]
        B --> C[cli_class.py]
    end
    
    subgraph "Orchestration Layer"
        C --> D[branch.sh]
        C --> E[safety.sh]
        C --> F[validate.sh]
        C --> G[config.sh]
    end
    
    subgraph "Sync Engine"
        C --> H[parallel_sync.py]
        C --> I[sync_prioritizer.py]
        C --> J[script_sync.py]
        H --> I
    end
    
    subgraph "Git Operations"
        D --> K[Git Commands]
        E --> K
        F --> K
        H --> K
        J --> K
    end
    
    subgraph "Analysis Tools"
        L[branch_analysis_check.sh] --> K
        M[update-all-branches.sh] --> K
        N[sync_orchestration_files.sh] --> D
        N --> G
    end
    
    style C fill:#ffd93d,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style H fill:#ff6b6b,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style M fill:#ff6b6b,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
```

