## Shell vs Python Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[New Feature Needed] --> B{Requires Git Operations?}
    
    B -->|Yes| C{Complex Logic?}
    B -->|No| D{System Integration?}
    
    C -->|Yes| E[Use Python]
    C -->|No| F{Fast Startup Critical?}
    
    F -->|Yes| G[Use Shell]
    F -->|No| E
    
    D -->|Yes| H{Simple Commands?}
    D -->|No| E
    
    H -->|Yes| G
    H -->|No| E
    
    E --> I[Benefits:<br/>- Testable<br/>- Maintainable<br/>- Type-safe]
    G --> J[Benefits:<br/>- Fast startup<br/>- Lightweight<br/>- Direct git access]
    
    style E fill:#6bcb77,stroke:#333
    style G fill:#6bcb77,stroke:#333
    style I fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#333
    style J fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#333
```

